{
  "stem": "9908.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "If you want to go in, you go and help yourself.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they dispersed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "You could see it on the-- on the village, it was also a village, [INAUDIBLE], was a village you could see it, how panicky they are, the-- the Poles, the Germans.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They started running out of the village and a lot of us followed them, but we didn't do anything.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But the villages, there lived a lot of Germans.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They knew that we're freed from the camps.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I swear to you, when you came out to the village, they would stand big barrels of potatoes and peels cooked, big barrels of eggs, big barrels of fruit, because they knew that we are going to come out and look for food.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "That's what we did.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "First, we did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I needed some shoes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "The German lady said, go ahead and choose what you want.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So I took some shoes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "We'd been there a few days.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "The Russians came in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We went-- there was a-- there was an order that state blow up the depot with the ammunition, and we all go with them.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "But [INAUDIBLE], they didn't have enough time, and they left us alive.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "We went to the village..",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "We got food.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Then the Czechs said it's dangerous to stay here.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "They took us to a school in the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Another day there were Russian soldiers already.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "They came in, I tell you, an army, exhausted, sick.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And they-- we, we, the haftlings, had to feed the Russian soldiers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "We-- we went into the village.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "They were scared of us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "They gave us whatever.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "They made ready for us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was-- we've been free.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As I saw the-- the Russian tore open the gate of the camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I stayed at the window, and I fell unconscious.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
